<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:15:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市因降息押注而上涨；聚焦印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-05/</link><description>亚洲股市周三上涨，而美元则保持稳定，原因是美国劳动力市场疲软，在本周重要的非农就业报告公布之前，强化了美联储在 9 月份降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>在银行诈骗中损失金钱的中国人抗议后被拘留数月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-who-lost-money-bank-fraud-detained-months-after-protest-2024-06-05/</link><description>该报道基于路透社对抗议录像、此前未报道的逮捕通知和采访的回顾，审视了自 2022 年以来在中国激增的一场经济抗议活动，在此期间，数十万人在房地产泡沫破裂中失去了房屋并成为受害者到投资诈骗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-who-lost-money-bank-fraud-detained-months-after-protest-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，中国强劲的服务业活动拉动就业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-robust-services-activity-drives-up-employment-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-05/</link><description>周三的一项私营部门调查显示，中国 5 月份服务业活动以 10 个月来最快速度加速，人员配备水平自 1 月份以来首次扩大，表明第二季度将持续复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-robust-services-activity-drives-up-employment-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查：投资者考虑选举和美国潜在宽松政策，新兴货币并未获得缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/no-relief-emerging-currencies-seen-investors-ponder-elections-potential-us-2024-06-05/</link><description>路透对货币分析师的调查显示，由于美联储不急于降息以及一些关键的全国大选结果，新兴市场货币今年将难以反弹。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:38:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/no-relief-emerging-currencies-seen-investors-ponder-elections-potential-us-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>随着交易员转向美国服务业数据，美元站稳脚跟</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-finds-footing-traders-turn-us-services-data-2024-06-05/</link><description>美元周三企稳，交易员削减了新兴市场风险较高的押注，同时等待加拿大利率决定和美国服务业数据。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:47:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-finds-footing-traders-turn-us-services-data-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>SEKO 赢得美国海关机构有条件恢复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/seko-wins-conditional-reinstatements-us-customs-agency-2024-06-05/</link><description>私营公司SEKO Logistics表示，美国海关与边境保护局（CBP）已有条件恢复其对两个重要国际贸易项目的参与，但仍未确定导致暂停的违规行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/seko-wins-conditional-reinstatements-us-customs-agency-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国人工智能芯片公司降级设计以确保台积电生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ai-chip-firms-downgrading-designs-secure-tsmc-production-sources-say-2024-06-04/</link><description>四位知情人士表示，一些中国人工智能芯片公司现在正在设计功能较弱的处理器，以在面临美国制裁的情况下保留台积电的生产权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 23:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ai-chip-firms-downgrading-designs-secure-tsmc-production-sources-say-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：政治、市场波动刺激市场上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 21:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>格兰霍姆称美国对中国汽车征收更高的关税对汽车制造商至关重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/granholm-says-new-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-crucial-us-auto-industry-2024-06-04/</link><description>美国能源部长詹妮弗·格兰霍姆周二表示，8月份按计划将中国电动汽车进口关税翻两番至100%以上，这对美国汽车行业的健康至关重要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 21:05:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/granholm-says-new-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-crucial-us-auto-industry-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员曼钦鼓励业界就电动汽车税收抵免起诉财政部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-sen-manchin-says-hes-encouraging-industry-sue-treasury-over-ev-tax-credits-2024-06-04/</link><description>美国参议员乔·曼钦 (Joe Manchin) 周二表示，他敦促美国公司就财政部根据《通货膨胀削减法案》(IRA) 为获得清洁能源税收抵免的公司制定的本地含量规则提起诉讼。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:07:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-sen-manchin-says-hes-encouraging-industry-sue-treasury-over-ev-tax-credits-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫对土耳其加入金砖国家的愿望表示欢迎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-welcomes-turkeys-reported-desire-join-brics-2024-06-04/</link><description>克里姆林宫发言人德米特里·佩斯科夫周二表示，俄罗斯欢迎土耳其希望成为金砖国家集团成员的愿望，并称该主题将列入该组织下次峰会的议程。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 12:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-welcomes-turkeys-reported-desire-join-brics-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国安全公司同方威视挑战欧盟针对涉嫌补贴的突击搜查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/chinese-security-firm-nuctech-challenges-eu-raids-over-alleged-subsidies-2024-06-04/</link><description>中国安全设备公司同方威视正就其荷兰和波兰办事处遭到突击搜查将欧盟委员会告上法庭，称没有证据支持其受益于非法国家支持的指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/chinese-security-firm-nuctech-challenges-eu-raids-over-alleged-subsidies-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国首次批准先进自动驾驶公开试验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gives-first-approvals-public-trials-advanced-autonomous-driving-2024-06-04/</link><description>作为加速自动驾驶汽车普及计划的一部分，中国已批准首批九家汽车制造商在公共道路上对采用先进自动驾驶技术的车辆进行测试。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 10:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gives-first-approvals-public-trials-advanced-autonomous-driving-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃将在欧盟规则出台之前颁发全球首张电动汽车电池护照</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-issue-worlds-first-ev-battery-passport-ahead-eu-rules-2024-06-04/</link><description>瑞典汽车制造商告诉路透社，沃尔沃汽车正在推出世界上第一张电动汽车电池护照，记录其旗舰产品 EX90 SUV 的原材料、零部件、回收成分和碳足迹的来源，该产品即将开始生产。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 10:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-issue-worlds-first-ev-battery-passport-ahead-eu-rules-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着利率、美元、石油下滑，华尔街的增长出现喘息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 10:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>